graph TB
    subgraph WVA["Workload Variant Autoscaler"]
        direction TB
        Controller["WVA Controller Manager<br/>(controller-runtime)"]
        SatEngine["Saturation Engine<br/>(optimization loop, 60s interval)"]
        SFZEngine["Scale-from-Zero Engine<br/>(InferencePool watcher)"]
        PromCollector["Prometheus Collector<br/>(cached PromQL queries)"]
        DirectActuator["Direct Actuator<br/>(replica patching)"]
        GPUDiscovery["GPU Capacity Discovery<br/>(GFD labels: NVIDIA/AMD/Intel)"]
        CMReconciler["ConfigMap Reconciler<br/>(dynamic config updates)"]
        IPReconciler["InferencePool Reconciler<br/>(pool endpoint tracking)"]

        Controller --> SatEngine
        Controller --> SFZEngine
        Controller --> CMReconciler
        Controller --> IPReconciler
        SatEngine --> PromCollector
        SatEngine --> GPUDiscovery
        SatEngine -->|stores decisions| DirectActuator
        SFZEngine -->|scale from 0| DirectActuator
    end

    %% CRDs
    User["Platform Admin / SRE"] -->|creates| VACR["VariantAutoscaling CR<br/>(llmd.ai/v1alpha1)"]
    VACR -->|watched by| Controller

    %% ConfigMap inputs
    ConfigMap["ConfigMaps<br/>(saturation thresholds,<br/>scale-to-zero settings)"] -->|watched by| CMReconciler

    %% InferencePool
    InferencePool["InferencePool CR<br/>(Gateway API)"] -->|watched by| IPReconciler

    %% External interactions
    PromCollector -->|PromQL queries<br/>9090/9091 TCP HTTPS| Prometheus["Prometheus /<br/>Thanos Querier"]
    DirectActuator -->|emits metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS| MetricsEndpoint["/metrics endpoint"]
    MetricsEndpoint -->|scraped by| Prometheus
    DirectActuator -->|patches replicas<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| ScaleTargets["Deployments /<br/>LeaderWorkerSets"]

    %% HPA/KEDA reads metrics
    Prometheus -->|custom metrics| HPAKEDA["HPA / KEDA"]
    HPAKEDA -->|scales| ScaleTargets

    %% GPU Discovery
    GPUDiscovery -->|reads GFD labels| Nodes["Cluster Nodes<br/>(GPU labels)"]

    %% Kubernetes API
    Controller -->|watches/updates<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SatEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SFZEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style PromCollector fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style DirectActuator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style GPUDiscovery fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CMReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style IPReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style VACR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style InferencePool fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ConfigMap fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style HPAKEDA fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ScaleTargets fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Nodes fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style MetricsEndpoint fill:#d4edda,stroke:#333
